Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.21,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.25,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:24.39,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:28.09,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:33.49,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.30,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:43.04,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:49.53,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Repaint the time that has been stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:57.25,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.19,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.50,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:18.77,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Recover the last piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:24.61,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those jerks wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toro Toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Toro Toro, aren't you? I'm Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toro Toro...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:52.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the character who helped\nwhen we slayed that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, it was this guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Megumi! I've told you not to bring\nanyone to the house, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of this room! Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O... Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Megumi! Don't bring shame upon\nyour big brother like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it! I'll make your meal and\nbring it right away, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's good, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This means you'll avoid falling into debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My repayment of my debts just\ngot further away though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about that stuff that cures the\nhikikomori state by eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:14.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If hikikomori could be cured by something like that,\NI wouldn't be suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saw the state my big brother's in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, he's hikikomori, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"If you join Mouseroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can get supplements that will\ncure your brother's reclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you can also attain a large income."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was drawn in with words like that too,\nin the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the reality is just as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how many supplements I fed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my brother's hikikomori condition didn't improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to meet my quotas,\nand my debt load kept increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I realize I'm stuck in a hole, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Maybe everything will start to spin into\nsome kind of a good rhythm!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:52.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With thinking like that, you can't grab\nany opportunity to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:04:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I truly wonder how long I'm supposed\nto keep up this kind of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother, your lunch is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:27.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My brother came to Tokyo two years before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:34.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got accepted to a university in Tokyo too,\nand we ended up living together,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:38.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but even by that time he had already been\nhikikomori for more than a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not going to college,\nand not working either,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he was just entirely absorbed\nin his online games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that impatience was a no-no\nin dealing with a hikikomori,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:55.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so my intention was to treat him with patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:05:00.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I even tried online games, to try to understand\na little better how he felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but very soon I had no free time\nto be playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father keeled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our living allowance got cut off,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the only way to get money for school and\nliving expenses was to earn it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was no way my brother could work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:25.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was no way my brother could work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so all I could do was strive on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't have the leisure of thinking\nabout respectability or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I chose the jobs where I could earn\nthe maximum possible income.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:41.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when it rains, it pours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every place I worked went out of business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I had never once gotten\npaid properly for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was at that time that someone from\NMouseroad approached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After that, it went just as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the end of my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied, Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:11.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as to why the deadly-earnest egomaniac\NClass Rep ended up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you understand, then go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because I need to go look for\na sucker to take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going to keep at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you already, I can't turn back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:44.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Sato. Our business is finished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HB38587&\shad0\bord1.3\3c&HD1CDCB&\frz12.743\fscx65\fscy70\move(187,42,135,7,0,2966)}Easy to Understand JUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an6\shad0\fscx71.25\fscy70\c&HC6C4CA&\3c&H685D71&\frz345.969\move(304,135,289,114,5,2966)}Sociophobia\NHIKIKOMORl:\NWhat the Family\NCan Do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My brother says he wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Online?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to login\nwith the above settings?\NCancel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Sa-To.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toro Toro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew he was playing this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I didn't know what kind of\ncharacter he was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:59.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what in the world he wants to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's the R.M.T.? Is it going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gave up games already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do R.M.T. either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got surprisingly little guts.\NYou had just started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet you never even succeeded\nin making one trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The entire world of games is\na big pack of lies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The stories of people making a lot of money at\NR.M.T. are just like urban legends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's absolutely impossible for beginners!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You realize that too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:41.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But maybe someday, somebody\nwill make a success of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That might be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It might be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A wonderful future of vast wealth\nmight be right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let it go already! What vast wealth?\NWhat wonderful future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at the reality! Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Class Rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's even turned to some shady pyramid scheme\nto earn money for both of your living expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her future is a black hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't what you're doing simple escapism?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're spending all your time\ndreaming comfortable dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and not facing up to reality, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd say such harsh things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, I was thinking we're both\nalike in not facing reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:48.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The truth is, I already understand what I should do\nnow, and what it would take to make my life go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've read 200 self-help books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've even thought of writing one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand it all, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of changing the routine of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I change it, something unforeseen could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even when my father keeled over,\nnobody told me to change my lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I realize it's no good to keep living as I am,\nbut I still want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to log out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though I know it can't happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm still thinking that one day, suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,an amazing surprise will occur and\neverything will start going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:43.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That feeling... Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can still turn back. Don't end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before you drag the people around you\ninto your misfortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you have to log out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&H484F4D&\shad0\pos(193,135)\c&HDFE1E1&}Logged Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sa... Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: Thanks for coming shopping\nwith me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: I still don't understand things\nin this world very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: So, I want you to choose\nwhich clothes look good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: Huh? This one?\NWait a minute. I'll try it on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: Well? Does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei: Really? Great! Okay, starting next\ntime, I'll appear in this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is an event scene that appears\nafter you've cleared the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can choose the heroine's default\noutfit for the next game here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a little gimmick to keep people from\ngetting bored after the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:02.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow... A lot of thinking goes into this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:08.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when the main narrative still isn't finished,\nthere isn't any point creating stuff like this, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whose fault do you think it is that it's not finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My work is at a halt because your scenario\nisn't progressing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't do anything else but make this kind of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to get started on the work\nfor the main narrative too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it! I'm telling you, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, today's the day I'll speak my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, after that hubbub with the pyramid scam,\nwhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I vow to seriously devote myself to game creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many weeks do you think\nhave passed since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been four weeks! Four weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:14:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But still the script hasn't progressed\nby more than a few kilobytes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFDFD5&\3c&HAE8678&\shad0\frz345.153\fscx75\fscy90\frx24\fry30\pos(250,31)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've passed the two-months-left point\nfor the winter Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this time we can't get away with\nfaking it with some sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the moment of truth for you too, Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to show whether you can carve out a life\nas a game creator or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, is it this late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It... It's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, if I'm intruding, it can wait till later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's fine. Please feed Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tuna again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:44.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's because the compound DHA found\nin tuna stimulates brain activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:50.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believe that eating tuna will unquestionably have a\npositive effect on your creative activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If eating tuna made me able to write the script,\NI wouldn't be having so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:15:01.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who do you have to thank, Sato, for the fact that\neven though your allowance has been cut in half,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you're not starving to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's not really like I begged you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you'd be okay with starving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or do you want to get swamped by debt, like\nthat committee-girl from your high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for this meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At Yuuhiyama Zoo, which has been a major topic of late,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a new animal exhibit has opened starting today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what was it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:40.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The "multilevel marketing" company\nthat you "cooled off" from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The headquarters of a company previously suspected\Nof being a disreputable "multilevel marketing" scheme
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"My"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:51.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouseroad, has been raided by the\NTokyo prosecutor's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm here at the Tokyo headquarters of Mouseroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouseroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tokyo prosecutor's office has raided Mouseroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Previously suspected of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something to wipe with... quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:04.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, are you watching the news?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouseroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:20.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, reports say that the total number of\NMouseroad members in Tokyo is over 15,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!\NFurthermore, reports say that the total number of\NMouseroad members in Tokyo is over 15,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:28.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, reports say that the total number of\NMouseroad members in Tokyo is over 15,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:37.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, on to Mouseroad, where a raid\nhas been ongoing for some days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Today investigators also entered the\nhome of executive Sukekiyo Sagawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where a foreign-made luxury car\nand other items were seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HEDE0DE&\shad0\3c&H806D75&\fscx83.75\fscy97.5\pos(266,114)}I'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HEDE0DE&\shad0\3c&H806D75&\fscx148.75\fscy162.5\pos(265,182)}I'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HEDE0DE&\an4\shad0\3c&H806D75&\fscx148.75\fscy162.5\pos(184,113)}I'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hungry! I'm hungry!\NI'm hntgp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening with my food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:47.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am I just going to die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother, I'm sorry I've been away for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's been a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you hungry? I'll make something right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Big Brother? Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4846A&\shad0\bord0\frz316.434\pos(255,120)\frx32\fry50}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The heroine's emotional line here is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is? I don't really think it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Players won't find this kind of thing satisfying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Players won't find this kind of thing satisfying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can say that, but we only have\none month until the winter Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can say that, but we only have\none month until the winter Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no time to be fixing it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's from Class Rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouseroad should be history by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's going to ask you\nto join a different pyramid scam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said Toro Toro's gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already tried everywhere I could think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were the only one left, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, so he hasn't contacted you either then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll inform the police too,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but if you get an e-mail or anything,\nplease let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I look horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I go back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, the pork-rice meal and\ntempura-rice meal are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, the pork-rice meal and\ntempura-rice meal are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going out on delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful while you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That boy's gotten a lot more energetic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean "boy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a man of plenty of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when he first came to this shop,\nhe looked just like a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saying stuff like, "I'll do anything\nif you'll give me food to eat."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's more, he said he was a hikikomori, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said he'd never actually worked in his life,\nwhich worried me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know what they say:\N"A person does what he's got to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:47.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they get hungry, human beings will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&H000000&\fscx211.25\fscy203.75\pos(191,94)\c&HFFA959&\shad0}Episode 19
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\3c&H000000&\c&HDF6D12&\fscx192.5\fscy217.5\pos(194,219)}Welcome to the Blue Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:21:59.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:24.87,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if this world were going to end tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.34,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Since it's you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.81,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you take the curt attitude of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:36.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"If so, that's okay with me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:40.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need to strain yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.86,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just sometimes would be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:48.95,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So lift up your face and look this way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.77,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:55.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Though it's a tiny world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:00.57,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,For some reason it's too big for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:04.18,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Though it's an endless world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:08.72,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,For some reason it's too small for these two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:15.99,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to laugh with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:21.53,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,In the irritating morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the name of the star?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A person's life is no more than trash, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:36.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you think you're God or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to Winter Days!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord2.3\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(193,80)\c&H8F794F&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord2.3\shad0\3c&H000000&\fscx186.25\fscy205\pos(193,214)\c&H715A23&}Welcome to Winter Days!
